Disable extension signature verification by default for CLI

Code-OSS builds lack Microsoft's signing infrastructure, causing
extension installation to fail with "Signature verification was not executed".
This patch changes the default from true to false, making signature
verification opt-in rather than opt-out for Code-OSS builds.


